========
bare-app
========

bare-app is a sample application that uses the stmm-input-gtk-dm library.
It prints out to the terminal the key(s) of all received events.
If the device is a joistick hat or a mouse button the keys are simulated.

Compile and run
---------------

mkdir build
cd build

cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug ..

make

./bare-app


